## Key differences from home (`epm-chatbot`)

| Aspect | Home (epm-chatbot) | Work |
|---|---|---|
| `route_query` caller | ADK LLM via ToolContext | Your REST handler directly |
| Context input | `tool_context.state` (ADK session) | Work session dict / context object |
| Shadow placement | Same pattern | Same pattern |
| Planner SDK | Gemini `generate_content` | OpenAI `chat.completions.parse` (from step 1.3) |
| Error handling | ADK wraps exceptions | Must catch manually (done in 1.5b block above) |
